美国财政部长[[史蒂芬·梅努欽|史蒂芬·梅努欽]]声明：“美国永远与香港人民站在一起，我们会利用我们的工具和权力，打击該等损害香港自治权之人士”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://home.treasury.gov/news/press-releases/sm1088|title=Treasury Sanctions Individuals for Undermining Hong Kong’s Autonomy|work=United States Department of the Treasury|date=2020-08-07|accessdate=2020-08-29|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807234822/https://home.treasury.gov/news/press-releases/sm1088|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

